<ul><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheSecretOfNIMH" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheSecretOfNIMH">The Secret of NIMH</a></em>: <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigBad" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigBad">Jenner</a>'s henchman Sullivan, who after being <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">slashed across the throat by Jenner, uses his last breath to throw his dagger into the evil rat's back</span>.
