<div class="indent"><strong>Rat:</strong> The boy is being held in an apple crate on top of a gun cabinet in the attic of Bean Annex. <br><strong>Fox:</strong> Would you have told me if I hadn't killed you first? <br><strong>Rat:</strong> Never.
